name: Fidelity Canadian High Quality ETF
longDescription: Fidelity Canadian High Quality Index ETF (Fund) seeks to replicate to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Fidelity Canada Canadian High Quality Index (Index). In order to achieve its investment objective Fidelity Canadian High Quality Index ETF normally invests its assets in the specific class or series of securities of the issuers that are included in the Fidelity Canada Canadian High Quality Index.
